@startuml
state WaitingForSale
state ItemsBeingAdded
state PaymentPending
state PaymentApproved
state SaleCompleted

WaitingForSale:wait for a new sale
ItemsBeingAdded:enter items one by one as they are selected by the customer
PaymentPending:move to payment after all items have been added
PaymentApproved:complete the sale immediately if the customer pays with cash
SaleCompleted:verify the payment if the customer chooses to pay by card or check
SaleCompleted:complete the sale once the payment is approved
WaitingForSale:return to waiting for the next customer after the payment has been finished

WaitingForSale --> ItemsBeingAdded:[*]
ItemsBeingAdded --> PaymentPending
PaymentPending --> PaymentApproved:pay with cash
PaymentPending --> SaleCompleted:pay by card or check
SaleCompleted --> SaleCompleted:payment approved
SaleCompleted --> WaitingForSale
@enduml
